<subSubSection id="C368652E935C8E01F2AAFE01FAC9FE1A" pageId="5" pageNumber="489" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935C8E01F2AAFE01FAC9FE1A" blockId="5.[151,1436,403,609]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">
<materialsCitation id="3B1A3CF8935C8E01F2AAFE01FAC5FE1A" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3798147329" collectorName="J. Serrano" determinerName="Z. Mylnar" pageId="5" pageNumber="489" specimenCount="3" typeStatus="holotype">
The 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935C8E01F2F1FE01FEFFFE66" box="[204,302,403,429]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">holotype</typeStatus>
is a male bearing the following labels: “male symbol”, “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935C8E01F183FE01FBCAFE66" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[958,1051,403,429]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="489" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lateralis">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935C8E01F183FE01FBCAFE66" box="[958,1051,403,429]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">lateralis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
m. in Hispania”, “ 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935C8E01F6CFFE01FA5FFE66" box="[1266,1422,403,429]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">HOLOTYPE</typeStatus>
”, “vidit 1974. 
<determinerName id="7E11DA61935C8E01F319FE25FE44FE1A" box="[292,405,439,465]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">Z. Mylnář</determinerName>
det. 1974” and “ 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935C8E01F06CFE25FD6DFE1A" box="[593,700,439,465]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">Holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935C8E01F0DCFE25FB9EFE1A" authority="Dejean, 1829" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[737,1103,439,465]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="489" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lateralis">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935C8E01F0DCFE25FC7EFE1A" box="[737,943,439,465]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">Harpalus lateralis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935C8E01F18AFE25FB9EFE1A" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[951,1103,439,465]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<collectorName id="26875373935C8E01F667FE25FB1BFE1A" box="[1114,1226,439,465]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">J. Serrano</collectorName>
vidit”
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C368652E935C8E01F2FAFE49FC47FDAA" pageId="5" pageNumber="489" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935C8E01F2FAFE49FAD8FDF6" blockId="5.[151,1436,403,609]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">
It was probably Mylnář who placed the label “ 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935C8E01F0D5FE49FC55FE3E" box="[744,900,475,501]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">HOLOTYPE</typeStatus>
”, as he examined types of Dejean’s collection (Mylnář, 1979). However, he did not publish any statement about the recognition of the 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935C8E01F65FFE6DFB19FDD2" box="[1122,1224,511,537]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">holotype</typeStatus>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935C8E01F6ECFE6DFABFFDD2" author="Fuente de la, J. M." box="[1233,1390,511,537]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489" refId="ref10490" refString="Fuente de la, J. M. (1927) Tablas analiticas para la clasificacion de los coleopteros de la Peninsula Iberica. Adephaga: I Cicindelidae, II Carabidae. J. Bosch, Barcelona, 415 pp." type="book" year="1927">Fuente (1927)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935C8E01F2AAFDB1FE92FDF6" author="Antoine, M." box="[151,323,546,573]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489" pagination="315 - 465" refId="ref10238" refString="Antoine, M. (1959) Coleopteres Carabiques du Maroc. Troisieme partie. Memoires de la Societe des Sciences Naturelles et Physiques du Maroc, Nouvelle Serie, Zoologie, 6, 315 - 465." type="journal article" year="1959">Antoine (1959)</bibRefCitation>
keyed the species. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935C8E01F021FDB1FD6CFDF6" author="Kataev, B. M." box="[540,701,547,573]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489" pagination="65 - 95" refId="ref11316" refString="Kataev, B. M. (1993) Zhuzhelitsy gruppy oblitus roda Harpalus Latr. Entomologicheskoe Obozrenie, 72, 65 - 95. [in Russian]" type="journal article" year="1993">Kataev (1993)</bibRefCitation>
also included a detailed illustration of the aedeagus.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935C8E01F2FAFDD5FC47FDAA" blockId="5.[151,1436,403,609]" box="[199,918,583,609]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">
The species is distributed in the Iberian Peninsula and 
<collectingCountry id="F3657635935C8E01F117FDD5FC42FDAA" box="[810,915,583,609]" name="Morocco" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">Morocco</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
